<l>tavaṟila rāyiṉun tāmvīḻvār meṉṟō</l>
<l> ḷakaṟali ṉāṅkoṉ ṟuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though free from defects, men feel pleased when they cannot embrace the delicate shoulders of those whom they love.</l>
